column1: NGR is 29 Dodington, a road in Whitchurch, hence the name given to the record. A B George MD, the observer, is noted as being based there. The building is still a surgery and it is noted that it has such for at least 120 years. There is a note "Whitchurh 800 yards N"; the church is about that distance N.
1874 readings crossed out with no explanation
